#, no-c-format
msgid "<option>--gametype</option> <replaceable> game</replaceable>"
msgstr "<option>--gametype</option> <replaceable> joc</replaceable>"

# skip-rule: punctuation-period-no
#. Tag: para
#: man-kpat.6.docbook:100
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Skip the selection screen and load a particular game type. Valid values are: "
"acesup, fortyeight, freecell, golf, grandfather, grandfathersclock, "
"normandy, klondike, mod3, simplesimon, spider, yukon"
msgstr ""
"Omet la pantalla de selecció i carrega un tipus de joc específic. Els valors "
"vàlids són: acesup, fortyeight, freecell, golf, grandfather, "
"grandfathersclock, normandia, klondike, mod3, simplesimon, spider i yukon."

